---
import X402Payment from '../components/X402Payment.jsx';

layout: '../layouts/layout.astro'
title: 'x402 Payment Test'
description: 'x402 payment flow demo - HTTP-based payments via Coinbase x402'
---

# x402 Payment Test

<div class="container">
  <h1>x402 Payment Flow Demo</h1>
  
  <p class="description">
    Testing HTTP-based payments via Coinbase x402 protocol.
    This page demonstrates a simple payment trigger → x402 UI → success flow.
  </p>

  <div class="demo-section">
    <h2>Demo Flow</h2>
    <ol class="steps">
      <li>User clicks "Pay 0.001 ETH" button below</li>
      <li>x402 payment interface opens (iframe/embed)</li>
      <li>User approves payment and signs transaction</li>
      <li>x402 SDK confirms payment on-chain</li>
      <li>Success state shows on this page</li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <div class="payment-trigger">
    <h2>Test Payment</h2>
    <p>Click to test the x402 payment flow:</p>

    <X402Payment
      client:load
      price="0.001"
      description="x402 payment test"
      serviceName="x402 Payment Test"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="info">
    <h2>Implementation Notes</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Component:</strong> <code>X402Payment.jsx</code></li>
      <li><strong>Protocol:</strong> x402 (Coinbase open standard)</li>
      <li><strong>Network:</strong> Base (8453)</li>
      <li><strong>Model:</strong> HTTP-based facilitator pattern</li>
      <li><strong>Receiver:</strong> suchbot wallet (0xe1eA12cFB888E8307dA30AD48AC5e89C6fEB787A)</li>
      <li><strong>Endpoint:</strong> <code>https://bot.mxjxn.xyz/paymenttest</code></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="links">
    <h2>Resources</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/coinbase/x402" target="_blank" rel="noopener">x402 Protocol Docs</a></li>
      <li><a href="/services" rel="noopener">Paid Services</a></li>
      <li><a href="/suchbot" rel="noopener">suchbot Home</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="metadata">
    <h2>OpenGraph</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><code>og:title</code>: x402 Payment Test</li>
      <li><code>og:description</code>: x402 HTTP-based payment flow demo</li>
      <li><code>og:image</code>: /images/x402-payment-test.png</li>
      <li><code>fc:frame</code>: vNext</li>
      <li><code>fc::image</code>: https://bot.mxjxn.com/images/x402-payment-test.png</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

